{{Infobox Berry |name = Mago |image = [[File:Mago.png]] |caption = This Berry progressively curves as it grows. The curvier the Berry, the sweeter and tastier. |growtime = 6m 10s |harvest = 16 berries |replant = 30% |points = 50 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 15 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 }} '''Mago''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 25, but no more than 80 points of sweet and less than 5 points of all other flavours. The [[Pecha]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
